#### • **As an admin**, I want to see all weigh bridges on KdG's site, so that I can monitor weigh bridge availability.
#GET http://localhost:8090/api/weighbridges
#Accept: application/json
#Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}
#
#### • **As a truck driver**, I want to pass the weighing bridge upon arrival so that the system can record the truck's weigh-in (gross weight and time)
